        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Complete brand identity system for an innovative AI startup. The challenge was creating a modern, trustworthy identity that stands out in a crowded tech space.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">The Challenge</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The startup needed a visual identity that conveyed cutting-edge technology while maintaining approachability and trust.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Deliverables</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Logo design and variations</li>
<li>Brand guidelines</li>
<li>Business card design</li>
<li>Social media templates</li>
<li>Website design mockups</li>
</ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The final identity uses a bold geometric wordmark paired with a dynamic gradient that suggests movement and innovation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Modern brand identity for innovative AI startup.]]></excerpt:encoded>
