        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Redesigned an outdated e-commerce platform to improve user experience and boost conversions. Focus on streamlined checkout and mobile-first design.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">The Solution</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Simplified navigation, improved product discovery, and reduced checkout steps from five to three. Mobile conversion rates increased by 40%.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>User research and persona development</li>
<li>Wireframing and prototyping</li>
<li>High-fidelity mockups</li>
<li>Responsive design system</li>
</ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[E-commerce redesign that increased mobile conversions by 40%.]]></excerpt:encoded>
